buyerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description: Welcome to your future home! This charming residence is conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. Step inside, where you will find a thoughtfully designed interior. The main living area welcomes you with its open-concept layout, creating a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen features built-in appliances and ample cabinets for storage. The master bedroom boasts a generous layout, plush carpeting, and a private en-suite bathroom. This delightful home also features the added benefit of solar panels, harnessing renewable energy to power your household! The backyard is a private retreat, offering an ideal space for outdoor activities or simply relaxing. The spacious enclosed patio is perfect for enjoying the weather year-round. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home! Schedule a tour today!
